{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"040bbdc403","title":"毛主席、朱总司令回答董其武等起义通电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8fa27fbedb","index":0,"year":1949,"month":9,"day":20,"articleId":"040bbdc403"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[{"id":"f96d65a0b5","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"040bbdc403","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"1949年9月19日原国民党绥远当局董其武将军发表起义通电。这是毛泽东为新华社摆写的电讯。"}],"contents":[{"id":"a8566e8537","type":"title","text":"毛主席、朱总司令回答董其武等起义通电”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"040bbdc403"},{"id":"f96d65a0b5","type":"paragraph","text":"【新华社北平二十日电】毛主席、朱总司令本日回答绥远董其武将军等九月十九日的起义通电如下董其武将军及在贵将军领导下的绥远军队全体官兵、政府工作人员和客界同胞们","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"040bbdc403"},{"id":"1a8aec0ae5","type":"paragraph","text":"看了你们九月十九日的声明，你们的立场是正确的。自从傅作义将军领导北平和平解放后，人民表示欢迎，反动派表示反对，反动派还企图破环绥远军民和平解放的努力，但是终归失败。你们已经率部起义，脱离反动派，站在人民方面了。希望你们团结一致，力求进步，改革旧制度，实行新政策，为建设人民的新绥远而奋斗。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"040bbdc403"},{"id":"2f7932afd5","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东朱德","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"040bbdc403"},{"id":"e6766166e2","type":"paragraph","text":"一九四九年九月二十日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"040bbdc403"}],"page":{"id":"dbf0c078cf","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"040bbdc403","start":269,"end":269}}}},"__N_SSG":true}